## 3. New Features Added

### `web_controller.py` — `BulkDeposit` API Endpoints

`BulkDeposit` existed in `models.py` and was seeded, but had no API surface. Added:

**`GET /api/web/bulk-deposits`**
- Lists all admin manual deposits
- Scoped by organization (`CommunityGroup → Organization` join)
- Returns: `id`, `adminName`, `userName`, `userEmail`, `walletId`, `totalPointsAwarded`, `itemCount`, `notes`, `createdAt`
- Auth: `@token_required` + `@admin_required`

**`POST /api/web/bulk-deposits`**
- Body: `{ walletId, totalPointsAwarded, itemCount, notes? }`
- Creates `BulkDeposit` record
- Credits `Wallet.points_balance` and `lifetime_points`
- Logs `Transaction` with `transaction_type='bulk_transaction'`, `reference_type='bulk_deposit'`
- Org-scope enforced: wallet user must belong to admin's organization
- Auth: `@token_required` + `@admin_required`

Also added `_serialize_bulk_deposit()` helper serializer.

