## 7. ERD Design Assessment

### Strengths (15 justified design decisions)

| Decision | Justification |
|---|---|
| `Wallet` separate from `User` | Single-responsibility; O(1) leaderboard reads via `lifetime_points` |
| `UserSecurity` separate from `User` | 2FA settings rarely read; avoids bloating the most-queried table |
| `OtpCode` as persistent DB table | Survives server restarts; works across multiple Gunicorn workers; auditable |
| `OrgAddress` + `OrgContact` flat | Replaces legacy `City` FK lookup; flat strings = fewer joins |
| ML-native `RecyclingItem` fields | `detected_class` + `confidence_score` directly maps YOLOv8 output |
| `RewardVariant` per-SKU stock | Realistic inventory management at variant level |
| `BulkDeposit` dedicated table | Separate audit trail for admin manual credits vs RVM sessions |
| `Transaction` structured references | `reference_type` + `reference_id` enables programmatic joins back to source |
| `RecyclingSession.wallet_id` direct FK | Old: `Session → Account → User → points`. New: `Session → Wallet`. One less join. |
| `User.community_group_id` direct FK | Removed `Account` indirection layer |
| `RVM.is_capacity_full` boolean | Maps directly to IR sensor HIGH/LOW output |
| `MaintenanceLog.status` enum | Can express `Cancelled` — impossible with old boolean `resolved` |
| `AdminLog.created_at` | Standardized timestamp naming across all tables |
| `TokenBlacklist` with `expires_at` | JWT revocation with cron-cleanable expiry |
| `LoginAttempt` table | Configurable lockout policies with per-attempt audit trail |

### Improvement Opportunities (Non-Blockers)

| Gap | Change | Status |
|---|---|---|
| `deactivated_at` on `User` and `Reward` | Added `DateTime nullable` to both models + ERD | ✅ Done |
| `avatar_url` on `User` | Added `String(500) nullable` + ERD | ✅ Done |
| `image_url` on `RewardVariant` | Added `String(500) nullable` + ERD | ✅ Done |
| OTP attempt counter on `OtpCode` | Added `attempts Integer default 0` + ERD | ✅ Done |
| `OrgContact` global unique scope | Changed to org-scoped `UniqueConstraint` for email and phone | ✅ Done |
| `NotificationSetting` dual-purposed | Kept as-is — acceptable trade-off | ⏭️ Deferred |

